Revision history for Perl extension BitTorrent.

0.10 Apr 26 03:54:07 2007
	- extraction of important information from tracker including filenames, filesize, hash string, announce url


0.01  Thu Mar 15 17:54:07 2007
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.23 with options
		-AXc -n BitTorrent
	- extraction of seeder leecher infos from given torrent url file with the help of extern application ( included in release )


todos in next minor versions:
	
	+ migrate away from extern application to pure perl 
	+ enhanced content / appilities of module


